"SHRED" PCB silkscreen logo, solid white single color, bold geometric sans-serif. "S" features horizontal offset ghost layer with 0.3mm displacement creating glitch echo effect, asymmetric vertical scale suggesting digital corruption. "H" crossbar formed by single continuous sine wave with three amplitude peaks. "R" in clean geometric form with leg terminating in downward arrow pulse. "E" vertical stem filled with six parallel horizontal lines evoking guitar strings, uniform 0.15mm spacing. "D" inner concentric arc echo forming reverb tail visualization, asymmetric height distortion intensified. 0.2mm uniform stroke width, clean terminals, compact horizontal lockup, 7mm optimal height, single color, manufacturing-ready, high contrast.
